        <updateDate>2008-10-17T19:32:49Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Gas Pump Fair Payment Act of 2008 - Amends the Truth in Lending Act to prohibit an electronic payment system network, for a specified six-month period, from requiring or permitting a merchant to pay an interchange, processing, or other fee in connection with any credit, charge, or debit card transaction involving a consumer purchase of motor vehicle fuel in excess of 1% of the cost of each gallon of such fuel.</p> <p></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
